<br>
Win98SE can't really handle more than 384 MB RAM realistically, 512MB RAM for sure.  Win2K can run up to 2GB for most versions, so you'll be sitting much better.<br>
<br>
Remember, Win98 is a 5 year old OS - do you have a 5 year old processor? <p><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><br>
